msgid "Auto-Detect BR Address"
msgstr "自动检测 BR 地址"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/jp_ipoe/config.js:52
msgid "Automatically apply configuration on router startup."
msgstr "路由器启动时自动应用配置。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/jp_ipoe/config.js:71
msgid ""
"Automatically derive all MAP-E parameters (BR, IPv4/IPv6 prefixes, EA/PSID/"
"offset) from the WAN6 IPv6 prefix, using the built-in OCN rule tables. No "
"need to run the MAP-E calculator. Disable to enter parameters manually."
msgstr ""
"使用内置的 OCN 规则表，从 WAN6 的 IPv6 前缀自动推导所有 MAP-E 参数（BR、IPv4/"
"IPv6 前缀、EA/PSID/offset），无需运行 MAP-E 计算器。关闭后可手动输入参数。"

