#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/jp_ipoe/config.js:47
msgid ""
"Configure OCN Virtual Connect (MAP-E) IPoE connection. This plugin uses an "
"existing IPv6 WAN (DHCPv6) interface and manages the MAP-E tunnel settings."
msgstr ""
"配置 OCN バーチャルコネクト（MAP-E）IPoE 连接。此插件使用已有的 IPv6 WAN"
"（DHCPv6）接口并管理 MAP-E 隧道设置。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/jp_ipoe/config.js:234
msgid "Could not resolve parameters."
msgstr "无法解析参数。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/jp_ipoe/config.js:155
msgid ""
"Detect the Border Relay address from the live MAP-E rule via mapcalc, then "
"optionally save it and re-apply. Only needed in manual mode; auto mode "
"derives the BR automatically."
msgstr ""
"通过 mapcalc 从实时 MAP-E 规则检测 Border Relay 地址，然后可选择保存并重新应"
"用。仅手动模式需要；自动模式会自动推导 BR。"

